    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《帽子先生大冒险》是一款非常有趣的横版闯关解谜游戏。极简的画风搭配丰富有趣的关卡玩法。游戏操作简单方便，每一关都有着不同的通关方式。脑洞大开的关卡谜题非常考验玩家的解谜能力和想象力！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在游戏中，玩家通过控制帽子先生，完成每一关所在房间对应的谜题后，就可以进入到下一关。我们后续也会更新新的关卡内容，欢迎大家来挑战游玩！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>如果你有任何问题、反馈，可以加入官方QQ群：639871910，将问题的描述、截图、录屏等内容提供给我们，我们会尽快查证并进行修复。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丰富有趣的关卡元素</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/ca79a516d72d30ff57753a06cd67fb5a.poster.avif?t=1645769112\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/ca79a516d72d30ff57753a06cd67fb5a.webm?t=1645769112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/ca79a516d72d30ff57753a06cd67fb5a.mp4?t=1645769112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>脑洞大开的通关方式</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/24310d4588106ac73ab8d8e67d035bc8.poster.avif?t=1645769112\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/24310d4588106ac73ab8d8e67d035bc8.webm?t=1645769112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/24310d4588106ac73ab8d8e67d035bc8.mp4?t=1645769112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>解谜玩法与横版玩法巧妙结合</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869200/extras/b034004578520419df22f302a3fdee6